{"diagram":{"elements":{"editorVersion":"V2","margin":{"childMarginW":44,"marginW":68},"comments":[],"watermark":"","data":{"right-content-index":"6"},"todoList":{},"enableFreeDrag":true,"textAutoWrapWidth":900,"showWatermark":false,"title":"5-10算法整理","hideSelf":false,"version":427,"structure":"mind_free","children":[{"parent":"root","customWidth":245,"lineStyle":{"randomLineColor":"#729B8D"},"children":[{"parent":"dc575ff9-ca26-434f-bd6e-405ff343ccc9","children":[{"parent":"bb6baf2f-b93d-458e-bce6-3fbabae6e918","children":[],"boundaries":[],"id":"42ced884-3a04-4d1f-9605-fb615a355157","title":"更新对象：状态价值表<b> V(s)</b><br>更新信号：完整 episode return <span class=\"equation-text\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-index=\"0\" data-equation=\"G_t\"><span></span><span>﻿</span></span><br>特点：必须等 episode 结束；不 bootstrap。"}],"link":{"id":"link_2b024f4f-d7e1-4592-9bcd-e28aac296b43","pageId":"page_6a16bd8c96d70229863cfef3","type":"t_link"},"id":"bb6baf2f-b93d-458e-bce6-3fbabae6e918","title":"MC prediction"},{"parent":"dc575ff9-ca26-434f-bd6e-405ff343ccc9","children":[],"id":"4187530e-b5db-4f82-ab43-8b806849b3e3","title":""},{"parent":"dc575ff9-ca26-434f-bd6e-405ff343ccc9","children":[],"id":"1848ac81-f1ab-40a8-a3a2-fa5a1bf937fa","title":""},{"parent":"dc575ff9-ca26-434f-bd6e-405ff343ccc9","children":[{"parent":"1f4a31ae-173f-45cc-a801-d0b00e172d37","children":[{"parent":"f71632ad-8a53-4073-a002-7c4af4148ed3","children":[],"id":"1ebb42cb-3230-47e1-94c8-79d6c4de8187","title":"第一步：按照当前策略 π 跑完整个 episode （同上）"},{"parent":"f71632ad-8a53-4073-a002-7c4af4148ed3","children":[],"id":"f23eabec-1898-4187-a522-057406ceaa8d","title":"第二步：episode 结束后，从后往前算回报 G（同上）"},{"parent":"f71632ad-8a53-4073-a002-7c4af4148ed3","children":[],"id":"e2b92492-8b4f-424d-bed6-29be360bd847","title":"第三步：关键变化：更新的是 <span class=\"equation-text\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-index=\"0\" data-equation=\"Q(St,At)\"><span></span><span>﻿</span></span>"}],"id":"f71632ad-8a53-4073-a002-7c4af4148ed3","title":"更新对象：动作价值表 <b>Q(s,a)</b><br>更新信号：完整 episode return <span class=\"equation-text\" data-index=\"0\" data-equation=\"G_t\" contenteditable=\"false\"><span></span><span>﻿</span></span><br>特点：先用完整回报评价动作，再用 $\\epsilon$ -greedy 改策略。"}],"link":{"id":"link_0a69488f-14de-459b-845d-b7046ca868a2","pageId":"page_6a16bd8c96d70229863cfef3","type":"t_link"},"id":"1f4a31ae-173f-45cc-a801-d0b00e172d37","title":"MC control"}],"style":{"font-size":"22px"},"id":"dc575ff9-ca26-434f-bd6e-405ff343ccc9","title":"Monte Carlo Methods"},{"parent":"root","note":"/ mean estimation，更新一般估计量，第六章主要引入了解决问题的思路 为后续的算法实际运行背书\n","lineStyle":{"randomLineColor":"#729B8D"},"children":[{"parent":"41f3b478-bae4-44da-a1e7-19dcea97faf2","children":[],"id":"f6a3d068-67c7-44fb-a81b-1cfdb3051693","title":"更新对象：一个未知期望或方程根的估计 w<br>更新信号：样本噪声下的误差。<br>特点：它不是一个具体 RL 算法，而是后面 TD / SGD 的数学骨架。"}],"style":{"font-size":"22px"},"id":"41f3b478-bae4-44da-a1e7-19dcea97faf2","title":"Robbins-Monro&nbsp;"},{"parent":"root","note":"","lineStyle":{"randomLineColor":"#EED484"},"children":[{"parent":"712ac52a-054d-482e-a518-42019af2a913","note":"它的任务不是学最优动作，而是：\n给定一个固定策略 π，估计这个策略下每个状态的价值 Vπ(s)。","children":[{"parent":"f51c17e6-fc8f-4673-a490-9f86dde29f18","children":[{"parent":"d6c06acf-08a9-40c1-bd7a-bfd73b2d6727","customWidth":978,"children":[],"id":"be6abe37-8757-425f-a60b-e096e10395b9","title":"我现在在状态 S，按照固定策略 π 选一个动作，走一步，得到奖励 R，进入下一个状态Snext<br>然后我立刻用 R+γV(Snext) 来修正当前状态 V(S)。"}],"id":"d6c06acf-08a9-40c1-bd7a-bfd73b2d6727","title":"更新对象：状态价值表 V(s)<br>更新信号：一步 TD error。<br>特点：不等 episode 结束；使用 bootstrap。"}],"id":"f51c17e6-fc8f-4673-a490-9f86dde29f18","title":"TD(0) state-value"},{"parent":"712ac52a-054d-482e-a518-42019af2a913","children":[{"parent":"91952326-2142-4ae6-8e78-b6a2f2c9b456","children":[{"parent":"8c3b6627-6335-4ebc-ba04-b6420c72819f","children":[],"id":"0f8a26de-baba-45ed-b37e-3296bce0cf75","title":"Sarsa 的关键是：A_next 真的来自当前$\\epsilon$-greedy  策略，所以它学的是当前策略自己的 $q_\\pi(s,a)$。如果 Q 变了，下一次 $\\epsilon$-greedy 选动作的概率也会变，这就是边评估边改进。"}],"id":"8c3b6627-6335-4ebc-ba04-b6420c72819f","title":"更新对象：动作价值表 Q(s,a)<br>更新信号：下一步真实采取动作带来的 TD target。<br>特点：on-policy；target 里用的是实际下一动作 $A_{t+1}$。"}],"id":"91952326-2142-4ae6-8e78-b6a2f2c9b456","title":"Sarsa，更新 q(s,a)"},{"parent":"712ac52a-054d-482e-a518-42019af2a913","children":[{"parent":"369b8b6c-3e2c-4ba6-8c9a-c6619dcd919d","children":[],"id":"52147756-8f4a-4fdb-8b3b-e1353449b64b","title":"更新对象：动作价值表 Q(s,a)<br>更新信号：下一状态下按当前策略求期望的 TD target。<br>特点：仍然是 on-policy，但不用一个实际 A_next，而是对所有动作加权平均。"}],"id":"369b8b6c-3e2c-4ba6-8c9a-c6619dcd919d","title":"Expected Sarsa"},{"parent":"712ac52a-054d-482e-a518-42019af2a913","children":[{"parent":"7b446133-d378-4924-a4db-b955bb86286d","children":[{"parent":"dd95e728-5291-42c6-9b94-14c1b8465f0d","children":[],"id":"fb251b2d-dae5-4d8b-9cf6-116079d3f5c0","title":"当 n=1，它就是 Sarsa；当 n 接近 episode 长度，它就越来越像 MC。"}],"id":"dd95e728-5291-42c6-9b94-14c1b8465f0d","title":"更新对象：动作价值表 Q(s,a)<br>更新信号：前&nbsp; n 步真实奖励，加上第 n 步后的 bootstrap。<br>特点：介于 one-step Sarsa 和 Monte Carlo 之间"}],"id":"7b446133-d378-4924-a4db-b955bb86286d","title":"n-step Sarsa"},{"parent":"712ac52a-054d-482e-a518-42019af2a913","children":[{"parent":"2a64a31f-1215-4ebe-b0a8-dfc7d5c7a4f0","children":[{"parent":"5c04ca4c-cd0e-41a5-8410-8b643fd8ad49","children":[],"id":"c78409ad-fb4b-447c-a20e-91c0f65b8b1e","title":"它和 Sarsa 的实际区别非常小，但意义很大：<br>Sarsa target:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;R + gamma * Q(S_next, A_next)<br>Q-learning target:R + gamma * max_a Q(S_next, a)"}],"id":"5c04ca4c-cd0e-41a5-8410-8b643fd8ad49","title":"更新对象：动作价值表 Q(s,a<br>更新信号：下一状态最大动作价值。<br>特点：off-policy；采样可以探索，但 target 假设下一步选 greedy action。"}],"id":"2a64a31f-1215-4ebe-b0a8-dfc7d5c7a4f0","title":"Q-learning"},{"parent":"712ac52a-054d-482e-a518-42019af2a913","children":[{"parent":"bd9ffc58-83ae-4944-a7c3-0993ed19e239","children":[],"id":"da42c4c6-9976-42a5-b155-efa4a01638c9","title":"更新对象：参数 w，不是单个表项。<br>更新信号：TD error。<br>特点：一个参数可能影响很多状态的估计值。","tags":[]}],"id":"bd9ffc58-83ae-4944-a7c3-0993ed19e239","title":"semi-gradient TD","tags":[{"color":"#fff","background":"rgb(231, 94, 91)","text":"时间顺序来看 这部分是后续章节引入"}]},{"parent":"712ac52a-054d-482e-a518-42019af2a913","children":[{"parent":"f0dfed13-bff8-4176-81ec-52b65c5bfce2","children":[],"id":"4436a95a-3a82-455c-a912-8e8e5d83f633","title":"更新对象：动作价值函数参数 w<br>更新信号：Sarsa TD error。<br>特点：把表格 Q(S,A) 换成函数 $\\hat q(S,A,w)$。","tags":[]}],"id":"f0dfed13-bff8-4176-81ec-52b65c5bfce2","title":"semi-gradient Sarsa","tags":[{"color":"#fff","background":"rgb(231, 94, 91)","text":"时间顺序来看 这部分是后续章节引入"}]}],"style":{"font-size":"22px"},"id":"712ac52a-054d-482e-a518-42019af2a913","title":"Temporal-Difference Methods"},{"parent":"root","customWidth":271.2,"lineStyle":{"randomLineColor":"#E19873"},"children":[{"parent":"31d611b9-044a-4be9-9b40-d0f35551cf4c","children":[{"parent":"2a7cac57-2746-4131-9a0e-c55b946f1ebd","children":[],"id":"4c91ecd3-81b9-4549-a8c7-7713f1078bcc","title":"更新对象：Q 网络参数 w<br>更新信号：Q-learning target，但 target 用另一个慢更新网络 w^-计算。<br>特点：experience replay + target network。"}],"id":"2a7cac57-2746-4131-9a0e-c55b946f1ebd","title":"DQN"}],"style":{"font-size":"22px"},"id":"31d611b9-044a-4be9-9b40-d0f35551cf4c","title":"Value Function Methods"},{"parent":"root","lineStyle":{"randomLineColor":"#DFE8D7"},"children":[{"parent":"ba68f125-3f3a-444d-9fdb-3a5d408b5eec","customWidth":1949,"lineStyle":{"lineType":"roundBroken"},"children":[],"style":{},"id":"49e00fb3-ae82-4baf-a087-051f7b09982d","title":"到这 我们从前面的 value-based 方法 转到 policygradient方法了。前面那些 TD、SARSA、DQN 主要是在学：V(s), Q(s,a) ，然后通过价值函数间接选动作。<br><br>而 REINFORCE 直接学策略：π(a∣s,θ)，也就是：神经网络直接输出每个动作的概率，然后更新策略参数 θ，让高回报动作出现概率更大"},{"parent":"ba68f125-3f3a-444d-9fdb-3a5d408b5eec","children":[{"parent":"43de4bc4-61bc-4829-afe1-37f20341a85f","children":[],"id":"449a2a41-1e37-406e-ae58-7bfbd0311590","title":"更新对象：策略参数 $\\theta$。<br>更新信号：完整 return G_t。<br>特点：不更新 value table；直接提高好动作的概率。"}],"id":"43de4bc4-61bc-4829-afe1-37f20341a85f","title":"REINFORCE"},{"parent":"ba68f125-3f3a-444d-9fdb-3a5d408b5eec","children":[{"parent":"695eeee4-faa2-4353-a1a0-c958ca9a6282","children":[],"id":"b0070462-ffbf-41a4-b2b8-863f0533687d","title":"更新对象：策略参数 $\\theta$，以及 baseline/value 参数 w<br>更新信号：G_t-b(S_t,w)<br>特点：baseline 不改变期望方向，但降低方差。"}],"id":"695eeee4-faa2-4353-a1a0-c958ca9a6282","title":"REINFORCE with baseline"}],"boundaries":[{"boundary":true,"parent":"ba68f125-3f3a-444d-9fdb-3a5d408b5eec","children":[],"range":"0,0","id":"e4d28221-68be-481e-8769-8cd7e81b04b8"}],"style":{"font-size":"22px"},"id":"ba68f125-3f3a-444d-9fdb-3a5d408b5eec","title":"Policy Gradient Methods","summaries":[]},{"parent":"root","lineStyle":{"randomLineColor":"#EED484"},"children":[{"parent":"e8a4c376-b930-4782-90ee-6a9b6f709800","children":[{"parent":"3ea5ed6d-e33a-4291-a74f-d89785f1aec8","children":[],"id":"16ae69be-528a-45a8-bf12-843e7c68763e","title":"更新对象：critic 参数 w和 actor 参数 \\theta<br>更新信号：critic 给出的 q(S,A,w)<br>特点：actor 不等完整 episode return，而是用 critic 的估计当质量信号"}],"id":"3ea5ed6d-e33a-4291-a74f-d89785f1aec8","title":"Q actor-critic"},{"parent":"e8a4c376-b930-4782-90ee-6a9b6f709800","children":[{"parent":"761cd396-bb49-45a9-8c7c-2263902861d9","children":[{"parent":"b8b5dbe6-b28c-43dd-9079-ed8ec87cb267","children":[{"parent":"cea48acc-fa14-460e-933a-d672fa1456bf","children":[],"id":"379fcc44-dce5-4ebf-b081-4c888dcafc83","title":""}],"id":"cea48acc-fa14-460e-933a-d672fa1456bf","title":"advantage"}],"id":"b8b5dbe6-b28c-43dd-9079-ed8ec87cb267","title":"更新对象：critic 的 w 和 actor 的 \\theta<br>更新信号：TD error $\\delta_t$，它可以看成一步 advantage 估计。<br>特点：critic 的 TD error 同时服务两个角色：更新 critic，也更新 actor。"}],"id":"761cd396-bb49-45a9-8c7c-2263902861d9","title":"advantage actor-critic / A2C"},{"parent":"e8a4c376-b930-4782-90ee-6a9b6f709800","children":[{"parent":"52552a4f-423d-42e2-a31a-cac2d623e582","children":[],"id":"58cd0e8d-e283-407d-a515-4e563772a4cb","title":"更新对象：critic 参数 w 和 actor 参数 $\\theta$。<br>更新信号：带 importance ratio 的 TD / policy-gradient signal。<br>特点：数据由 behavior policy $b$ 生成，但 actor 想更新 target policy $\\pi_\\theta$。"}],"id":"52552a4f-423d-42e2-a31a-cac2d623e582","title":"off-policy actor-critic"},{"parent":"e8a4c376-b930-4782-90ee-6a9b6f709800","children":[{"parent":"177bd950-bd89-4199-b015-28565f01ee6e","children":[],"id":"a9dc21f1-85ce-469c-99b0-4aaa29007bc6","title":"更新对象：actor 参数 $\\theta$ 和 critic 参数 $w$。<br>更新信号：critic 对动作的梯度 $\\nabla_a q(s,a,w)$。<br>特点：actor 不输出动作概率，而是直接输出动作。"}],"id":"177bd950-bd89-4199-b015-28565f01ee6e","title":"deterministic policy gradient / DPG"}],"id":"e8a4c376-b930-4782-90ee-6a9b6f709800","title":"actor-critic"}],"freeChildren":[{"parent":"root","lineStyle":{"randomLineColor":"#E19873"},"children":[],"pos":{"x":916.3751304197102,"y":-1018.504762888987},"style":{"font-size":"14px"},"id":"5ee4e2b1-af7c-4819-9b37-84fde4463605","title":"用同样的东西(Gt) 近似两个看似不同的东西（V/Q）","free":true}],"root":true,"theme":{"connectionStyle":{"lineType":"dashed","lineColor":"#C7654E","lineWidth":2},"skeletonId":"mindmap_curve_green-default","summaryTopic":{"lineStyle":{"lineType":"roundBroken","lineWidth":2},"shape":"radiansRectangle","summaryLineColor":"#C7654E","background":"autoColor","summaryLineType":"curve_complex","font-size":"14px","selfStyle":true,"border-color":"autoColor","summaryLineWidth":2},"autoColor":true,"floatingTopic":{"lineStyle":{"lineType":"roundBroken","lineWidth":2},"shape":"radiansRectangle","background":"autoColor","font-size":18,"border-color":"autoColor"},"version":"v6.1.1","colorList":["#729B8D","#EED484","#E19873","#DFE8D7"],"common":{"textAlign":"left","bold":false,"italic":false},"colorMinorId":"mind-style1","background":"#ffffff","centerTopic":{"lineStyle":{"lineType":"curve","lineWidth":3},"shape":"radiansRectangle","background":"#C7654E","font-weight":"bold","font-size":30,"border-color":"#C7654E"},"w1":1,"childTopic":{"lineStyle":{"lineType":"roundBroken","lineWidth":2},"shape":"underline","font-size":22,"border-width":2,"border-color":"autoColor","childBgOpacity":"0.16","anticipateBackground":"autoColor"},"w2":12,"boundaryStyle":{"lineType":2,"dasharray":"6,3","lineColor":"#C7654E","fill":"#C7654E","opacity":"0.1","lineWidth":2},"secTopic":{"lineStyle":{"lineType":"roundBroken","lineWidth":2},"shape":"radiansRectangle","background":"autoColor","font-size":18,"border-color":"autoColor"},"colorCardId":"system"},"id":"root","isBackground":true,"lines":{"1f435765-4c84-4bce-9e48-6a5273788199":{"startAngle":90,"endAngle":270,"start":{"x":"0.5","y":"1.0","index":3},"label":"从v到q","pts":[],"points":[],"realEnd":{"x":681.266993713379,"y":133.25},"from":"bd9ffc58-83ae-4944-a7c3-0993ed19e239","end":{"x":"0.5","y":"0.0","index":1},"styles":{},"to":"f0dfed13-bff8-4176-81ec-52b65c5bfce2","id":"1f435765-4c84-4bce-9e48-6a5273788199","realStart":{"x":681.266993713379,"y":89.25}},"c989eb9d-5748-4ef8-91b9-d85b670bd0db":{"startAngle":170.61378468735478,"endAngle":183.57924836716617,"start":{"x":"0.0","y":"1.0","index":4},"label":"更新目标不一样 MC更新的是完整的GT 而TD是Rt+1+γV(St+1)所以不需要等episode结束 自然是bootstrap","pts":[{"x":-819.7724921276323,"y":136.26036628844236},{"x":-831.6296349847751,"y":-50.31106228298614}],"points":[{"x":-509.2724921276323,"y":-740.9896337115576},{"x":-482.02963498477504,"y":-173.06106228298614}],"realEnd":{"x":188.00000000000003,"y":-131.15},"from":"dc575ff9-ca26-434f-bd6e-405ff343ccc9","end":{"x":"0.0","y":"0.3","index":1},"styles":{},"to":"712ac52a-054d-482e-a518-42019af2a913","id":"c989eb9d-5748-4ef8-91b9-d85b670bd0db","realStart":{"x":188,"y":-856.25}},"30063e72-116a-43e9-a9e0-dfaec4626a90":{"startAngle":10.420213059467882,"endAngle":190.4202130594679,"start":{"x":"0.5","y":"1.0","index":3},"label":"","pts":[],"points":[],"realEnd":{"x":1081.6084637530435,"y":-951.8380962223202},"from":"42ced884-3a04-4d1f-9605-fb615a355157","end":{"x":"0.5","y":"0.0","index":1},"styles":{},"to":"5ee4e2b1-af7c-4819-9b37-84fde4463605","id":"30063e72-116a-43e9-a9e0-dfaec4626a90","realStart":{"x":954.3000000000001,"y":-975.25}},"904b889d-2483-40ec-b5b5-75ca03a2d1ad":{"startAngle":95.44033203100551,"endAngle":275.4403320310055,"start":{"x":"0.5","y":"1.0","index":4},"label":"从v到q","pts":[],"points":[],"realEnd":{"x":671.8000000000001,"y":-377.75},"from":"f51c17e6-fc8f-4673-a490-9f86dde29f18","end":{"x":"0.5","y":"0.0","index":2},"styles":{},"to":"91952326-2142-4ae6-8e78-b6a2f2c9b456","id":"904b889d-2483-40ec-b5b5-75ca03a2d1ad","realStart":{"x":677.8000000000001,"y":-440.75}},"493e2425-c7b5-4978-a9ea-c57910fa4b98":{"startAngle":65.94334293409274,"endAngle":311.75008050512287,"start":{"x":"0.6","y":"1.0","index":3},"label":"MC prediction 是“评价当前策略”。 MC control 是“评价动作，并让策略越来越倾向于好动作”","pts":[{"x":44.273972132618724,"y":79.0348140628895},{"x":54.72851758716416,"y":-64.60154957347413}],"points":[{"x":626.8739721326187,"y":-916.2151859371105},{"x":622.3285175871642,"y":-863.8515495734741}],"realEnd":{"x":582.52,"y":-819.25},"from":"bb6baf2f-b93d-458e-bce6-3fbabae6e918","end":{"x":"0.6","y":"0.0","index":2},"styles":{},"to":"1f4a31ae-173f-45cc-a801-d0b00e172d37","id":"493e2425-c7b5-4978-a9ea-c57910fa4b98","realStart":{"x":600.52,"y":-975.25}},"304c9fff-a801-4e27-95b5-fd9af43b52db":{"startAngle":118.35560207132654,"endAngle":298.3556020713267,"start":{"x":"0.6","y":"1.0","index":3},"label":"抽到vs当前策略平均","pts":[],"points":[],"realEnd":{"x":656.3000000000001,"y":-268.75},"from":"91952326-2142-4ae6-8e78-b6a2f2c9b456","end":{"x":"0.5","y":"0.0","index":1},"styles":{},"to":"369b8b6c-3e2c-4ba6-8c9a-c6619dcd919d","id":"304c9fff-a801-4e27-95b5-fd9af43b52db","realStart":{"x":691.9200000000001,"y":-334.75}},"45926abd-eae8-42da-bd97-4dd239552990":{"startAngle":157.78478933114005,"endAngle":337.7847893311401,"start":{"x":"0.5","y":"1.0","index":4},"label":"","pts":[],"points":[],"realEnd":{"x":1026.3000000000002,"y":-889.25},"from":"5ee4e2b1-af7c-4819-9b37-84fde4463605","end":{"x":"0.5","y":"0.0","index":2},"styles":{},"to":"f71632ad-8a53-4073-a002-7c4af4148ed3","id":"45926abd-eae8-42da-bd97-4dd239552990","realStart":{"x":1081.6084637530435,"y":-911.8380962223202}}}}},"meta":{"exportTime":"2026-05-27 21:30:38","member":"","diagramInfo":{"creator":"","title":"5-10算法整理","category":"mind"},"id":"525439372849","type":"ProcessOn Schema File","version":"1.0"}}